        </div>

        <div class="project">
            <h3>Oony</h3>
            <p>
                In 2010, I co-founded
                <a href="https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/oony">Oony</a>,
                a shopping guide with automated recommendations based on users’
                preferences, which grew to feature over 3 million products
                across 15 countries. The project was originally launched as
                <a href="https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/weegoh"
                    >Weegoh</a
                >
                in 2008, the first location-based social network in Latin
                America, before pivoting to become Oony.
            </p>
